WEBVTT

00:15.640 --> 00:18.230
They're really blood diamonds.

00:19.510 --> 00:21.510
They must be real, right?

00:22.700 --> 00:24.060
How much are they worth?

00:24.550 --> 00:26.870
We're the only ones
who know how many there are.

00:27.650 --> 00:28.860
Should we steal one each?

00:28.860 --> 00:30.720
I didn't expect this from you.

00:31.250 --> 00:32.700
You're so smart.

00:36.830 --> 00:38.390
What if

00:39.710 --> 00:41.490
we're infected? What should we do?

00:42.010 --> 00:43.190
Are you scared?

00:45.030 --> 00:46.280
Aren't you scared?

00:47.510 --> 00:49.240
I told you before

00:49.930 --> 00:52.060
what I fear the most.

00:53.400 --> 00:55.710
I'm more afraid of

00:55.710 --> 00:57.850
being away from him than what he does.

00:58.500 --> 01:00.020
I'm with him at the moment

01:00.020 --> 01:01.260
so I'm not afraid of anything at all.

01:21.620 --> 01:23.520
Are you crazy?

01:23.850 --> 01:24.750
Get out!

01:24.750 --> 01:26.039
I'm under quarantine.

01:39.070 --> 01:41.039
It's me, isn't it?

01:48.820 --> 01:50.960
I'm a little scared this time.

01:58.050 --> 01:59.430
Shi Jin.

02:01.190 --> 02:03.760
Please get him out of here.

02:04.510 --> 02:06.120
I'm not leaving.

02:08.100 --> 02:09.720
I'm going to stay here.

02:11.840 --> 02:14.390
I'm going to stay with you.

02:25.800 --> 02:27.300
I'm a confirmed M3 patient

02:28.190 --> 02:30.160
and you've been
in contact with that patient.

02:37.670 --> 02:39.200
I'm a doctor.

02:41.880 --> 02:43.600
And your superior
as well. This is an order.

02:46.450 --> 02:47.600
Leave!

03:02.730 --> 03:04.620
What's going to happen to Myung Joo?

03:05.020 --> 03:07.760
The fatality rate is over 50 percent.

03:08.900 --> 03:11.770
I heard it's as bad as Ebola.

03:11.770 --> 03:13.190
Am I right?

03:13.190 --> 03:14.980
You're right.

03:14.980 --> 03:17.780
Is she going to die or live?

03:18.660 --> 03:20.540
There's no guarantee
with a disease like this.

03:21.320 --> 03:25.829
However, a young and healthy patient like Lieutenant Yoon

03:26.270 --> 03:28.340
is more likely to survive.

03:28.870 --> 03:30.540
Her immune system is good.

03:34.360 --> 03:35.920
Thank you.

03:36.360 --> 03:38.190
Immune storm?

03:38.190 --> 03:40.280
Isn't being young and healthy a good thing?

03:40.280 --> 03:41.550
Because she's got a good immune system?

03:42.600 --> 03:44.530
It's quite ironic.

03:44.900 --> 03:47.420
Her good immune system might harm her.

03:47.550 --> 03:48.850
What should we do now?

03:50.290 --> 03:51.860
Is there anything that we can do?

03:52.450 --> 03:56.110
I'll fight it in every possible way.

03:57.130 --> 03:58.700
I'll try not to be defeated.

04:00.200 --> 04:03.850
The war on viruses is a doctor's war.

04:05.990 --> 04:08.020
I'm glad that I have
a reliable doctor like you.

04:11.930 --> 04:14.430
We have a confirmed M3 patient.

04:14.760 --> 04:16.060
As of now, medical zone is the main medical facility

04:16.060 --> 04:20.070
to treat patients infected by the M3 virus.

04:20.070 --> 04:21.370
We're going to use the ICU

04:21.370 --> 04:24.070
as an isolation ward for the M3 patients.

04:24.070 --> 04:27.000
If you follow the regulations the medical team provides

04:27.000 --> 04:28.850
and pay attention to your hygiene,

04:28.850 --> 04:30.520
we can prevent more people from getting infected.

04:30.520 --> 04:31.820
We shouldn't be too relaxed

04:31.820 --> 04:34.250
or too scared.

04:34.250 --> 04:35.510
This is a hospital

04:35.510 --> 04:38.400
and we have patients to treat.

04:38.400 --> 04:40.640
Let's focus on our job

04:40.640 --> 04:42.490
Under these circumstances.

04:54.600 --> 04:55.960
Why do you need a laptop?

04:56.390 --> 04:57.860
I'm bored.

04:57.860 --> 04:59.220
I'm going to play computer games.

05:00.690 --> 05:02.800
and use up all the items that I have saved.

05:03.340 --> 05:04.650
There's no use saving them.

05:04.650 --> 05:08.090
38.7. Your fever isn't dropping.

05:09.230 --> 05:10.530
It'll sting.

05:11.320 --> 05:13.820
You're good at drawing blood.

05:13.820 --> 05:15.390
And it worked just one time.

05:15.390 --> 05:17.080
Not at first time.

05:17.710 --> 05:19.590
When I was a trainee nurse,

05:19.590 --> 05:22.380
I destroyed the arm of my friend, who was a med student.

05:22.380 --> 05:23.600
You remember.

05:25.500 --> 05:28.370
I feel thankful to him
whenever I draw blood.

05:29.590 --> 05:31.010
Hold it tight.

05:33.180 --> 05:34.580
Why are you being so sweet?

05:35.180 --> 05:36.440
Do you think I might die?

05:37.670 --> 05:39.000
Do you think I'm positive?

05:42.870 --> 05:45.510
As far as I'm concerned, you caught a cold

05:45.510 --> 05:47.260
and special symptoms were faked..

05:48.430 --> 05:49.380
If you need anything, call me.

05:53.140 --> 05:54.640
What if I miss you?

05:59.460 --> 06:00.990
I'll be back before that happens.

06:16.970 --> 06:20.000
Aren't you dying of boredom there?

06:23.750 --> 06:25.330
I'm sorry to do this
to you at a time like this.

06:25.970 --> 06:27.090
I’m sorry.

06:27.090 --> 06:29.080
If you're sorry, get out of there healthily.

06:29.970 --> 06:31.500
Goof up all you want,

06:31.940 --> 06:34.130
but become a strong man.

06:36.020 --> 06:37.770
How's Myung Joo?

06:38.670 --> 06:39.790
Is she okay?

06:39.790 --> 06:42.210
She's not a patient yet.
She's still a doctor.

06:42.570 --> 06:43.920
She's busy

06:43.920 --> 06:45.490
taking care of Mr. Jin and herself.

06:48.720 --> 06:50.530
What about you?

06:51.380 --> 06:53.900
I'm okay.

06:53.900 --> 06:55.690
Tell her not to worry about me.

06:55.920 --> 06:57.300
Channel three.

07:03.630 --> 07:04.890
Talk to her.

07:05.750 --> 07:09.570
I'm repaying you
for letting me talk to Dr. Kang.

07:11.630 --> 07:12.930
Thank you.

07:13.600 --> 07:14.950
Take care.

07:27.250 --> 07:29.050
This is Yoon Myung Joo.

07:29.610 --> 07:31.870
Sergeant Seo Dae Young, do you copy?

07:40.550 --> 07:41.659
Copy that.

07:42.060 --> 07:45.370
Huh? It's you, Seo Dae Young.

07:46.430 --> 07:48.440
How are you feeling?

07:53.620 --> 07:55.510
I miss you.

07:58.820 --> 08:00.570
Have you eaten?

08:01.320 --> 08:03.420
I miss you.

08:08.340 --> 08:09.920
How are you feeling?

08:15.860 --> 08:17.280
Fool.

08:17.700 --> 08:19.140
I’ve already told you how to answer.

08:22.770 --> 08:23.850
I miss you.

08:35.760 --> 08:39.630
Have you eaten?

08:41.370 --> 08:43.350
I miss you.

08:50.570 --> 08:52.490
I know.

08:55.390 --> 08:57.220
Are you crying?

09:02.620 --> 09:04.550
Do you remember

09:05.330 --> 09:07.210
the white dress I was wearing

09:07.680 --> 09:09.540
when we met for the second time?

09:10.420 --> 09:12.040
Do you remember what you told me back then?

09:12.500 --> 09:14.680
You told me I looked like a ghost.

09:16.710 --> 09:19.450
Now I remember that incident all of a sudden

09:19.450 --> 09:21.170
and think it might have been an omen.

09:21.950 --> 09:24.160
If I die now, that'll be proven to be true.

09:24.800 --> 09:26.340
This is too much to take in.

09:29.410 --> 09:30.820
You're an angel,

09:33.500 --> 09:35.310
Yoon Myung Joo.

09:36.910 --> 09:40.880
Since the moment you came into my life, you've been an angel.

09:42.230 --> 09:44.120
I want you to know that.

09:51.080 --> 09:53.530
You've been sweet since I was sick.

09:57.530 --> 09:59.360
Whether I'm a ghost or an angel

10:00.440 --> 10:02.190
I'm dead either way.

10:28.860 --> 10:31.090
Until we have the test results,

10:31.090 --> 10:32.840
the medical zone is going to be closed off.

10:33.480 --> 10:37.050
We've opened up a temporary clinic for regular patients for now.

10:37.860 --> 10:40.580
When can we get
the vaccines that we asked for?

10:40.580 --> 10:43.040
I contacted city headquarters last night.

10:43.040 --> 10:44.690
They should be here
tomorrow at the latest.

10:45.150 --> 10:47.390
Have you checked
who the confirmed patients

10:47.390 --> 10:48.820
were in contact with so far?

10:48.820 --> 10:50.520
We've made a list
of everyone who contacted with Mr. Jin,

10:50.520 --> 10:52.080
the first confirmed patient,

10:52.080 --> 10:54.430
and sent it to the UN.

10:54.430 --> 10:56.410
So they can isolate and diagnose them.

10:56.410 --> 10:57.600
If you look at the list of names...

10:57.600 --> 10:58.520
Hey! Stop!

10:58.520 --> 10:59.430
Don't come any closer.

10:59.430 --> 11:00.950
Stay behind the table over there.

11:03.900 --> 11:05.020
How's Lieutenant Yoon?

11:05.020 --> 11:06.120
Is she okay?

11:06.120 --> 11:08.250
- She seems to be fine at the moment.
- Does she?

11:08.970 --> 11:09.690
Well.

11:09.690 --> 11:11.770
Move her to the US Army hospital immediately.

11:12.160 --> 11:14.180
I've already sent
them an official letter.

11:14.180 --> 11:15.690
Let's move her as soon as possible.

11:15.690 --> 11:16.950
The medical zone is
the main medical facility

11:16.950 --> 11:19.470
designated by the UN
for M3 virus patients.

11:19.880 --> 11:20.860
We can't move her.

11:20.860 --> 11:22.160
Tell me something I don't know.

11:22.700 --> 11:24.060
Just listen to me

11:24.530 --> 11:25.980
and move her right away!

11:25.980 --> 11:26.800
Before things get out of control!

11:26.800 --> 11:28.600
I'm following protocol in case of an epidemic breakout.

11:28.600 --> 11:30.620
You don't want to go home?

11:33.490 --> 11:34.980
What if things don't get better soon?

11:34.980 --> 11:35.880
Do you want to remain here?

11:35.880 --> 11:36.870
We're fighting against

11:36.870 --> 11:38.610
an intangible enemy.

11:38.610 --> 11:40.150
It's an unknown enemy,

11:40.150 --> 11:41.430
but it's real.

11:41.430 --> 11:43.210
If we don't follow protocol,

11:44.300 --> 11:45.660
no one is safe.

11:45.660 --> 11:48.360
Why are you being right and

11:48.360 --> 11:49.350
making me feel ashamed of myself?

11:50.960 --> 11:52.010
Okay. I take it back.

11:52.340 --> 11:53.490
But remember,

11:54.670 --> 11:56.240
if any one of you gets sick,

11:56.240 --> 11:57.410
I can't go home.

11:57.980 --> 12:00.390
No one gets sick! Do you understand?

12:00.390 --> 12:01.360
Yes, sir!

12:02.690 --> 12:03.770
Sir!

12:04.680 --> 12:06.750
There were two Korean citizens have been confirmed to infect

12:06.750 --> 12:08.360
the M3 virus, a level 4legal infectious disease in Mouru,

12:08.360 --> 12:13.820
where was recently hit by a huge earthquake.

12:13.820 --> 12:17.590
Those confirmed Korean citizensare one male and one female...

12:17.590 --> 12:18.820
I'm calling Mo Yeon.

12:18.820 --> 12:20.210
I'm calling Dr. Song.

12:20.210 --> 12:22.330
Why isn't she answering her phone?

12:22.560 --> 12:24.330
Dr. Song's phone's turned off.

12:24.720 --> 12:25.710
Hello?

12:25.710 --> 12:26.760
Did Chi Hoon answer his phone?

12:27.910 --> 12:30.020
Mother, it's me.

12:30.640 --> 12:32.260
Did you see the news?

12:34.380 --> 12:37.040
It's an epidemic this time.

12:37.710 --> 12:39.430
Why didn't they come back when I sent the charter?

12:39.430 --> 12:41.970
Why drive me crazy for over a month?

12:42.330 --> 12:43.830
Driving you crazy?

12:44.140 --> 12:45.920
I've already gone crazy.

12:46.300 --> 12:47.040
You're here.

12:47.040 --> 12:48.280
Yes, I'm here.

12:48.280 --> 12:51.590
Because you're not doing your job, I came here.

12:51.590 --> 12:52.820
Why are you still here

12:52.820 --> 12:54.420
wasting time?

12:54.420 --> 12:56.370
Hire a charter and go to Uruk right now.

12:56.370 --> 12:57.390
Why should I go there?

12:57.390 --> 12:59.690
There's an epidemic breakout.

12:59.690 --> 13:00.930
"Why should I go there?"

13:00.930 --> 13:02.600
You don't care about your employees?

13:02.900 --> 13:04.840
You're the head of this hospital.

13:06.230 --> 13:08.340
Where the hell did you send my son Chi Hoon?

13:08.340 --> 13:09.700
Get Chi Hoon back here

13:09.700 --> 13:11.980
within 24 hours.

13:11.980 --> 13:14.430
Auntie, please. Can you let go of...

13:14.430 --> 13:16.330
What are you doing? Stop her.

13:16.610 --> 13:17.550
Well...

13:18.140 --> 13:20.410
How dare you tell
my daughter-in-law what to do?

13:20.410 --> 13:21.460
She's pregnant!

13:21.460 --> 13:24.160
I feel like I'm a widow.

13:25.660 --> 13:28.330
Did you hear that? Vacate this building immediately!

13:28.330 --> 13:29.960
I'm not a friend

13:29.960 --> 13:31.220
of your mother's anymore.

13:32.260 --> 13:33.730
Auntie! Stop!

13:34.320 --> 13:36.510
I'll bring him back. I will.

13:36.510 --> 13:37.870
I promise that I'll bring him back.

13:37.870 --> 13:39.600
If he arrives here tomorrow,

13:39.600 --> 13:44.020
will that make you feel better? Tomorrow?

13:45.620 --> 13:46.780
Dr. Pyo,

13:46.780 --> 13:48.010
can you do me a favor?

13:48.950 --> 13:50.270
I can't find some of the articles

13:50.270 --> 13:52.220
in medical journals on the Internet.

13:52.220 --> 13:54.310
There're too many to scan.

13:54.310 --> 13:55.840
I'll just send pictures.

14:22.620 --> 14:24.190
What's all these?

14:26.890 --> 14:28.590
Do doctors study even when they're sick?

14:28.590 --> 14:30.620
Soldiers fight wars
even when they're sick.

14:31.550 --> 14:33.620
I guess you're right.

14:34.890 --> 14:36.350
Do you want some more snacks?

14:36.820 --> 14:38.580
Do you want something else to munch on?

14:38.580 --> 14:40.430
No. I'm curious about this disease.

14:40.430 --> 14:42.100
That's why I'm eating.

14:42.100 --> 14:44.720
I need stamina to stay focused.

14:46.770 --> 14:48.040
I'm fighting a war,

14:48.040 --> 14:50.370
in a way.

14:52.350 --> 14:53.330
I enjoyed my lunch.

14:53.690 --> 14:54.630
Thank you.

14:55.260 --> 14:57.730
I hope you win. Sir!

15:16.650 --> 15:17.970
Can that guy survive?

15:21.450 --> 15:23.240
He's regained consciousness,

15:23.240 --> 15:25.690
but his breathing is very unstable.

15:25.690 --> 15:27.430
The next couple of days are critical.

15:27.430 --> 15:29.740
It’s said that they foundmany diamonds in his stomach.

15:29.740 --> 15:31.480
Wow!

15:33.200 --> 15:35.850
That’s right.. What I saw was true.

15:37.240 --> 15:38.940
How much would these diamonds be worth?

15:39.930 --> 15:43.160
There were 30 of the highest grade two-carat diamonds.

15:44.390 --> 15:45.220
About two million dollars?

15:45.220 --> 15:48.550
Two million dollars...

15:49.680 --> 15:57.650
Two million dollars! Would I risk my life for two million dollars?

16:12.190 --> 16:13.030
It's been a while.

16:14.270 --> 16:16.920
I heard you went to headquarters.

16:17.810 --> 16:19.230
When can we get the blood test results?

16:20.840 --> 16:23.020
Probably tomorrow afternoon.

16:23.590 --> 16:24.750
They'll send a fax.

16:25.500 --> 16:27.940
That's quicker than I thought. That's good.

16:28.520 --> 16:29.460
Right.

16:33.310 --> 16:34.440
Speaking of drawing blood,

16:36.050 --> 16:37.750
what's your blood type?

16:39.620 --> 16:40.940
Your ideal type?

16:45.890 --> 16:47.080
Go on.

16:48.290 --> 16:49.300
A pretty type?

16:51.360 --> 16:52.970
One more.

16:53.430 --> 16:54.510
A cute type?

16:57.900 --> 17:01.510
I give up. I give up.

17:01.510 --> 17:03.000
Did you like it?

17:03.360 --> 17:06.150
You made silly jokes to make me feel better.

17:06.150 --> 17:08.119
This time, I want to make you feel better.

17:11.109 --> 17:12.430
Don't worry about me.

17:13.069 --> 17:14.780
Please defeat this epidemic

17:14.780 --> 17:16.130
as quickly as possible.

17:16.970 --> 17:18.380
I want to hold your hands and hug you.

17:19.800 --> 17:20.990
It’s hard for me to get through such period.

17:21.670 --> 17:24.190
Is that all you can think about at a time like this?

17:24.190 --> 17:26.839
It was a joke. I wanted to make you feel better.

17:26.839 --> 17:28.089
I don't believe you.

17:29.100 --> 17:31.040
I have to go to fight this epidemic.

17:34.520 --> 17:36.070
What's your blood type?

17:36.850 --> 17:39.300
A type who wants
a life sentence in your jail?

17:40.590 --> 17:41.610
Go!

17:41.610 --> 17:43.090
Go to fight the epidemic. Now!

17:43.090 --> 17:44.000
I've got more.

17:44.000 --> 17:46.170
Go on. Please go.

17:55.430 --> 17:56.890
Her breathing and body temperature are normal.

17:58.860 --> 18:00.600
You're all better.

18:00.600 --> 18:02.690
You'll go to a safe place tomorrow.

18:02.690 --> 18:05.970
A bad virus is going around here.

18:08.660 --> 18:09.830
Here we go again.

18:09.830 --> 18:12.360
This is Lieutenant Yoon. The power's gone out.

18:12.360 --> 18:13.910
Isn't the backup generator working?

18:14.910 --> 18:15.630
It's not the generator.

18:15.630 --> 18:16.850
It's the wire.

18:16.850 --> 18:18.030
I'll be there right now.

18:18.380 --> 18:19.540
We're in the dining room...

18:22.000 --> 18:23.640
Mr. Jin's respirator!

18:24.170 --> 18:25.240
Can you take over?

18:32.450 --> 18:33.880
What's wrong with you?

18:49.880 --> 18:51.200
- Sedatives!
- Okay.

18:57.300 --> 18:58.210
What's going on?

19:00.500 --> 19:01.350
I'm coming in.

19:01.350 --> 19:02.400
Don't come in!

19:02.980 --> 19:04.480
You might get infected!

19:06.070 --> 19:08.290
We'll take care of him.

19:08.290 --> 19:10.820
Focus on fixing the generator.

19:11.280 --> 19:13.130
10 minutes! Give us 10 minutes!

19:13.830 --> 19:14.990
Ok.

19:34.900 --> 19:36.060
Stethoscope!

19:40.360 --> 19:41.200
Are you okay?

19:44.840 --> 19:45.990
His heartbeat is too weak.

19:46.030 --> 19:47.120
Get him a manual resuscitation bag.

19:50.700 --> 19:52.230
One, two, three!

19:53.010 --> 19:54.010
One, two, three!

19:54.010 --> 19:55.450
-He bit you!
-One, two, three!

19:55.450 --> 19:56.570
This is serious.

20:01.230 --> 20:02.370
What's going on?

20:02.370 --> 20:03.040
Are you okay?

20:03.040 --> 20:05.090
Don't talk to me. It's too hard.

20:05.340 --> 20:07.020
One, two, three!

20:07.020 --> 20:07.870
I'll hold it!

20:08.790 --> 20:10.110
How long has it been?

20:10.440 --> 20:11.650
Two minutes.

20:11.820 --> 20:13.290
He bit Dr. Lee's arm.

20:13.290 --> 20:14.090
Chi Hoon!

20:14.090 --> 20:15.520
Not now!

20:15.520 --> 20:18.470
One, two, three!

20:18.470 --> 20:22.740
One, two, three!

20:48.860 --> 20:50.570
You know that you're at a high risk

20:50.570 --> 20:52.940
of getting infected because of this.

20:54.440 --> 20:55.540
Yes.

20:57.510 --> 21:01.440
If it weren't you,

21:01.440 --> 21:02.530
he would've died.

21:08.970 --> 21:10.990
You're a real doctor now.

21:12.490 --> 21:13.630
I'll draw blood.

21:16.550 --> 21:19.160
I've finished cleaning up. We have to go.

21:19.160 --> 21:20.920
Thank you.

21:32.660 --> 21:36.040
Is he going to get sick?

21:36.650 --> 21:38.420
I hope he won't.

21:39.470 --> 21:41.940
He's going to be isolated for now.

21:42.440 --> 21:45.720
Dr. Lee, you were really cool earlier.

21:49.160 --> 21:51.050
You looked like a doctor just now.

21:53.130 --> 21:54.330
Let's go.

22:09.330 --> 22:10.440
Why are you crying?

22:11.160 --> 22:12.280
Did I hurt you?

22:13.760 --> 22:15.100
Where did it hurt?

22:15.940 --> 22:17.690
No.

22:18.860 --> 22:20.330
I'm okay.

22:24.360 --> 22:26.880
I'm okay now.

22:28.870 --> 22:31.320
Now I can call her.

22:33.410 --> 22:34.960
What are you talking about?

22:35.630 --> 22:37.210
How do you feel, Chi Hoon?

22:42.080 --> 22:43.050
Isolated?

22:44.110 --> 22:46.900
Are you infected with

22:47.350 --> 22:48.920
the M3 virus?

22:48.920 --> 22:52.360
It's possible, but I'm not sure yet.

22:53.210 --> 22:54.820
I think

22:54.820 --> 22:56.550
I'm becoming a real doctor.

22:57.340 --> 22:58.580
You haven't called me
for over a month.

22:58.580 --> 23:00.720
What are you talking about? You fool!

23:01.300 --> 23:03.280
Do you know how worried I've been?

23:04.860 --> 23:06.010
I thought I was getting a divorce

23:06.010 --> 23:08.110
with a baby in my stomach.

23:08.110 --> 23:09.320
You know what?

23:10.470 --> 23:12.180
That's not such a bad thing.

23:12.720 --> 23:14.310
You can get stinking rich

23:14.310 --> 23:15.780
with alimony.

23:15.780 --> 23:17.010
Hey!

23:19.940 --> 23:21.380
I love you, Hee Eun.

23:22.300 --> 23:25.270
I really, really love you, Hee Eun.

23:25.910 --> 23:27.410
Now you sound like
Lee Chi Hoon I know.

23:30.560 --> 23:31.750
You're back.

23:46.930 --> 23:48.800
They just left downtown.

23:48.800 --> 23:51.020
They'll get to the UN camp in three hours.

23:51.020 --> 23:53.040
Please take care of the children.

23:57.830 --> 23:58.720
Dr. Kang.

24:00.030 --> 24:01.250
Fax.

24:01.250 --> 24:03.900
The blood test results came in. They all came back negative.

24:03.900 --> 24:04.970
Really?

24:07.090 --> 24:08.260
That's great.

24:08.260 --> 24:09.460
Does Captain Yoo know?

24:09.460 --> 24:11.740
Captain Yoo gave me this fax.

24:11.740 --> 24:14.480
He went to release Sergeant Seo.

24:22.030 --> 24:23.310
She's been bossing people around,

24:23.310 --> 24:26.000
finished a bowl of rice, and fell asleep.

24:26.540 --> 24:28.740
I knew she'd be feisty.

24:29.940 --> 24:31.690
In rare cases, even if you're infected,

24:31.690 --> 24:35.850
symptoms don't appear.

24:36.460 --> 24:38.350
She's a rare kind.

24:39.140 --> 24:41.260
I really hope that she won’t be infected..

24:44.700 --> 24:47.180
By the way, did you hear the news?

24:48.300 --> 24:49.870
What do you mean?

24:49.870 --> 24:51.940
Because I took prompt measures,

24:51.940 --> 24:55.010
there aren't any more
patients in the city.

24:55.010 --> 24:57.310
And after the vaccinations are done,

24:57.310 --> 25:01.450
the warning level will be dropped from "caution" to "attention."

25:01.450 --> 25:06.100
The UN sent an official thank you note

25:06.140 --> 25:08.770
to the captain of Mouru Unit,

25:10.600 --> 25:13.870
which is me.

25:18.250 --> 25:19.790
Did you hear what I said?

25:21.950 --> 25:23.110
What did you say?

25:24.370 --> 25:26.090
Well, thanks to

25:26.090 --> 25:28.030
my prompt actions...

25:28.820 --> 25:29.970
This is Snoopy!

25:29.970 --> 25:34.380
We have an emergency case in the dining room.

25:34.380 --> 25:36.890
Alpha Team. Come and help us.

26:34.140 --> 26:36.150
It's good to see familiar faces.

26:37.320 --> 26:38.880
Former comrade,

26:39.280 --> 26:40.840
my lifesaver,

26:43.050 --> 26:45.890
and my little red rose.

26:46.700 --> 26:48.360
How are you, Fatima?

26:50.390 --> 26:52.570
Are they here to get tested for the M3 virus?

26:53.300 --> 26:54.440
Virus?

26:55.140 --> 26:57.180
Don't worry, Doctor.

26:57.180 --> 26:59.350
Already tested negative.

26:59.350 --> 27:03.860
The US Army came in advance and tested me.

27:04.740 --> 27:06.990
Apparently, I can't be sick.

27:06.990 --> 27:08.520
They love me more than

27:08.520 --> 27:09.560
when I was a Delta Force captain.

27:09.560 --> 27:12.840
Be quick and watch your mouth.

27:12.840 --> 27:17.750
Don't ever say that we're on the same side.

27:18.230 --> 27:19.290
Okay.

27:20.160 --> 27:22.140
We can catch up next time.

27:22.140 --> 27:25.020
I'm just here to see my Korean friend.

27:25.020 --> 27:27.400
He was very ill.

27:27.400 --> 27:29.440
Mr. Jin.

27:29.440 --> 27:31.070
Can I see him now?

27:32.730 --> 27:34.310
Your friends

27:34.310 --> 27:36.640
aren't welcome here.

27:36.640 --> 27:38.420
So,

27:39.180 --> 27:40.510
Let him go.

27:40.510 --> 27:41.680
Well...

27:43.970 --> 27:46.190
I can always catch up with him next time.

27:46.190 --> 27:48.520
But just one question.

27:49.420 --> 27:51.530
I heard my stuff is here.

27:52.180 --> 27:55.150
It's very expensive.

27:56.820 --> 27:58.250
Sparkly.

27:59.070 --> 28:02.630
And women adore it.

28:04.050 --> 28:05.710
Can I see that instead?

28:09.280 --> 28:15.410
There is not a lost and found.

28:15.410 --> 28:18.370
I'll give you 10 seconds to get out of my face.

28:20.270 --> 28:23.620
Ten, nine...

28:24.700 --> 28:27.100
You should've opened him up.

28:47.140 --> 28:48.760
It's immune globulin.

28:49.010 --> 28:51.240
I couldn't visit my friend empty-handed.

28:51.910 --> 28:54.080
This is for you, Doctor.

29:00.210 --> 29:01.860
Please bring him back.

29:02.440 --> 29:05.240
I have a lot to say to him.

29:10.450 --> 29:11.880
Looks like everyone's busy.

29:11.880 --> 29:15.190
So we shall go.

29:24.520 --> 29:26.580
I think they figured out this operation.

29:26.580 --> 29:28.200
They also knew what we're capable of.

29:30.330 --> 29:32.170
Tighten security near the barracks.

29:44.220 --> 29:45.470
Is he the jerk

29:45.470 --> 29:47.380
who was trying to harm her?

29:48.780 --> 29:50.600
Can you take care of Dr. Song?

29:50.600 --> 29:53.060
I'll stay with her.

29:53.640 --> 29:55.120
We have the test results.

29:57.140 --> 30:00.910
What?

30:11.580 --> 30:13.180
The test results came out.

30:13.630 --> 30:17.050
Really? I'm officially free then.

30:18.940 --> 30:19.960
Let me get out of here.

30:20.200 --> 30:22.620
Where are you going?
I didn't tell you the result yet.

30:22.620 --> 30:25.040
High fever, headache,
and chest pains accompanied by coughing.

30:25.040 --> 30:27.880
The early symptoms are similar to Ebola
and the M3 virus.

30:27.880 --> 30:29.330
but my skin's still fair.

30:29.330 --> 30:31.470
And I still find you pretty.

30:31.520 --> 30:33.100
So my eyesight is fine.

30:34.620 --> 30:37.190
This is also some sort of virus.

30:37.710 --> 30:39.150
Haven't you ever had the flu before?

30:42.830 --> 30:46.080
Yes, you fool! You caught a cold.

30:46.530 --> 30:47.690
I was worried!

31:24.960 --> 31:26.930
What is it? Let me go.

31:27.260 --> 31:28.650
You held me first.

31:28.800 --> 31:31.040
That's why I let you go.

31:31.040 --> 31:32.140
Let me go.

31:32.840 --> 31:35.520
Catch a cold. You catch a cold, too.

31:35.520 --> 31:36.970
You immature fool!

31:42.780 --> 31:43.930
Read this first.

31:44.550 --> 31:45.600
While I was locked up, I had to make

31:45.600 --> 31:48.730
the most difficult decision of my life

31:49.110 --> 31:50.620
and I finally have the answer.

31:58.580 --> 32:01.420
What? What is it?

32:07.350 --> 32:08.790
Cefotaxime?

32:10.050 --> 32:11.500
It's a cure for Lyme disease.

32:11.700 --> 32:13.370
Where's Dr. Kang?

32:18.870 --> 32:20.790
According to the report

32:21.070 --> 32:22.170
from the Medipeace doctors who worked

32:22.170 --> 32:24.010
in West Africa in 2007 and 2011,

32:24.010 --> 32:27.220
it cured an average 85 percent of patients.

32:27.220 --> 32:30.500
54 out of 63 and 73 out of 85.

32:30.710 --> 32:33.250
By the way, how did you figure this out?

32:33.250 --> 32:36.120
Isn't it quite far removed from the common efficacy of Cefotaxime?

32:36.160 --> 32:37.130
I cross-examined

32:37.130 --> 32:38.830
the M3 virus's gene analysis

32:38.830 --> 32:42.040
and the chemical formula
and the molecular mass

32:42.040 --> 32:44.030
of every kind of antibiotic.

32:44.030 --> 32:44.760
Really?

32:44.760 --> 32:45.980
I'm kidding.

32:46.400 --> 32:48.830
I just went through all the articles about M3 by year.

32:48.830 --> 32:50.730
Every single one of them.

32:51.670 --> 32:53.260
I admire you, Dr. Song.

32:53.990 --> 32:55.650
Let's do this.

32:56.140 --> 32:58.940
But on the list of the medical supplies,

32:58.940 --> 33:00.120
we don't have it.

33:00.850 --> 33:02.240
Can you call Daniel now and...

33:02.240 --> 33:03.260
I already have.

33:03.510 --> 33:04.140
Already?

33:04.140 --> 33:05.700
It'll come with the other vaccines.

33:06.020 --> 33:07.040
If you'll excuse me.

33:11.960 --> 33:12.900
Did you two have a fight?

33:12.900 --> 33:14.660
This is what people call "playing hard to get."

33:15.540 --> 33:18.520
Geeze. She was worried about you.

33:39.530 --> 33:40.880
Sir!

33:43.700 --> 33:45.350
Dad.

33:47.120 --> 33:48.830
I'm really sick.

33:50.620 --> 33:53.060
Have you heard about me?

33:54.100 --> 33:55.770
I have.

33:57.770 --> 33:59.860
Then why haven't you called me?

34:00.960 --> 34:03.400
You only have a 50 percent chance of surviving.

34:05.260 --> 34:07.590
As your father and your superior,

34:08.080 --> 34:11.510
there's nothing I can do.

34:13.750 --> 34:15.949
I didn't know what I should do.

34:18.780 --> 34:21.040
I was waiting for you to call me.

34:22.690 --> 34:26.080
I feel so helpless at the moment.

34:26.659 --> 34:28.350
I'm not going to lose.

34:28.870 --> 34:30.330
I'm going to fight this.

34:30.719 --> 34:32.250
Don't worry, Dad.

34:33.070 --> 34:35.060
Sure.

34:36.820 --> 34:38.530
That's my girl. Please win this fight.

34:40.830 --> 34:43.110
If I do, can you do two things for me?

34:46.389 --> 34:49.820
Just two things?

34:51.460 --> 34:58.570
First...I want you to forgive me.

35:02.000 --> 35:03.670
Before I came here,

35:05.630 --> 35:07.460
I threatened that you'd lose

35:07.460 --> 35:12.840
both your daughter and Lieutenant Yoon Myung Joo.

35:18.340 --> 35:20.200
I'm sorry, Dad.

35:24.820 --> 35:28.490
Okay. Just get better, okay?

35:31.770 --> 35:33.600
What's the other one?

35:37.310 --> 35:39.310
If I get better...

35:40.290 --> 35:42.170
if I survive this disease,

35:45.820 --> 35:48.500
don't make Sergeant Seo retire from the army.

35:50.740 --> 35:53.290
Please don't. Please.

35:59.140 --> 36:01.000
I heard everything.

36:02.540 --> 36:05.280
Yoon Myung Joo! Leave us.

36:12.620 --> 36:15.310
I don't want a sergeant as a son-in-law.

36:15.310 --> 36:17.370
You need to leave the army.

36:18.080 --> 36:20.200
Sergeant Seo Dae Young

36:20.200 --> 36:22.070
was ordered to date you.

36:22.300 --> 36:23.390
This is official, ma'am!

36:23.390 --> 36:25.830
Did he really say that we could date?

36:25.830 --> 36:27.330
Yes, ma'am.

36:29.780 --> 36:31.910
I was so happy to be with him.

36:33.370 --> 36:34.970
So I pretended that I didn't hear that.

36:38.220 --> 36:39.680
I'm sorry, Dad.

36:43.140 --> 36:49.830
You're worried about me but I'm worried about him.

36:53.550 --> 36:55.820
Now you sound like my daughter.

36:56.480 --> 36:59.260
My daughter's usually disobedient.

37:08.600 --> 37:10.430
I'll call you later, Dad.

37:11.100 --> 37:13.490
It's time for my shot.

37:14.230 --> 37:15.690
Bye.

37:23.760 --> 37:25.130
Lieutenant Yoon!

37:26.390 --> 37:27.510
Yoon Myung Joo!

37:40.220 --> 37:41.490
Come on!

37:46.240 --> 37:47.390
Her temperature's 41 degrees.

37:47.730 --> 37:49.540
The Antifebrile isn't working at all.

37:49.540 --> 37:51.530
The situation what we have concerned finally arrived..

37:51.530 --> 37:52.520
Is her immune system overreacting?

37:52.520 --> 37:54.050
Yes, it's a immune storm.

37:54.110 --> 37:55.420
Give her some steroids.

37:55.830 --> 37:57.200
Fill the tub with ice.

38:03.010 --> 38:04.030
Before her body destroys itself,

38:04.030 --> 38:04.860
if we want to keep her alive,

38:04.860 --> 38:05.980
we need to lower her fever first.

38:08.840 --> 38:11.020
Right now, we have to deal with symptoms

38:11.020 --> 38:12.980
whenever they appear.

38:12.980 --> 38:14.220
I'm hoping the medicine

38:14.220 --> 38:16.720
that Dr. Song found will work.

38:16.720 --> 38:18.440
Isn't the medicine here yet?

38:18.440 --> 38:19.900
It'll be here with the vaccines.

38:19.900 --> 38:21.620
So, it'll be here soon...

38:21.960 --> 38:22.970
It's Daniel.

38:23.660 --> 38:24.930
Hello. Are you here?

38:25.950 --> 38:28.060
What? What are you talking about?

38:33.430 --> 38:36.690
The vehicle that was delivering medicine was hijacked.

38:37.630 --> 38:40.840
Lieutenant Yoon's medicine was there as well.

38:40.840 --> 38:42.130
Who the hell...

38:42.130 --> 38:43.640
If we can't get that medicine within an hour,

38:43.640 --> 38:45.330
it'll be too late.

38:45.330 --> 38:46.820
It'll take at least four hours

38:46.820 --> 38:48.310
to get more.

38:48.310 --> 38:49.730
Is there any other way?

38:50.000 --> 38:51.520
If we catch the jerk who stole it...

38:51.800 --> 38:52.740
Communication classes.

38:52.740 --> 38:53.390
Hello. I'll call you back...

38:53.390 --> 38:54.640
Captain Big Boss! Come in!

38:54.640 --> 38:58.310
This is Argus! Over!

38:58.310 --> 39:00.430
What the hell are you doing?

39:02.470 --> 39:04.350
Bring back the medicine. Now!

39:04.350 --> 39:07.250
I'm a businessman. Not a soldier.

39:07.250 --> 39:10.940
Instead of making orders, let's make a deal.

39:11.400 --> 39:14.720
Bring me the diamonds if you want to get your medicines back.

39:17.060 --> 39:20.370
I think I know where Myung Joo's medicine is.

39:32.710 --> 39:33.610
This is Snoopy.

39:34.360 --> 39:35.630
We've secured everyone's location.

39:45.280 --> 39:46.360
Where's Argus?

39:46.360 --> 39:47.790
He's busy.

39:48.420 --> 39:49.510
Where is it?

40:13.120 --> 40:14.470
Okay.

40:18.110 --> 40:19.510
Let him go.

40:26.400 --> 40:27.680
All right.

40:28.830 --> 40:30.690
Thank you for the diamonds.

40:34.820 --> 40:36.990
Stay right there, you jerk!

40:49.040 --> 40:50.940
If it hurts, scream. It's okay.

40:52.310 --> 40:53.680
It's okay.

40:53.680 --> 40:54.900
I can handle this.

40:55.390 --> 40:57.890
Hang in there.

40:59.960 --> 41:00.790
Dr. Kang!

41:00.790 --> 41:01.410
I think the medicine is here.

41:01.410 --> 41:02.410
Stay with her.

41:10.140 --> 41:11.500
What are you guys doing?

41:16.010 --> 41:17.250
Official duty.

41:17.650 --> 41:20.600
This girl you're taking care of is under arrest

41:20.600 --> 41:25.170
for dealing stolen medicine in the black market.

41:25.170 --> 41:28.140
Her accomplice has already confessed.

41:39.710 --> 41:41.600
There must be a misunderstanding.

41:41.820 --> 41:45.530
She didn't steal it. We gave those medicines to Fatima.

41:45.530 --> 41:49.580
I gave them to her,
so you have no reason to arrest her now.

41:49.580 --> 41:52.260
Even if you had given it to her,

41:52.260 --> 41:56.160
she's still under arrest for dealing in the black market.

41:56.160 --> 42:00.280
Were you that foreign doctor who was at the scene?

42:02.140 --> 42:03.300
Science is so advanced.

42:03.300 --> 42:05.570
I don't understand
why we don't have a cure.

42:05.990 --> 42:07.590
Because it doesn't sell.

42:07.590 --> 42:09.190
If it doesn't sell, they can't make money.

42:09.190 --> 42:10.750
If they can't make money, they won't make it.

42:10.750 --> 42:12.150
People are dying.

42:12.150 --> 42:14.480
They won't make a product because they can't make money?

42:14.480 --> 42:16.450
That's why people like us

42:16.450 --> 42:18.710
do things we aren't allowed to do

42:18.710 --> 42:20.690
and go places we're not allowed to go.

42:21.690 --> 42:23.080
We want to change the world.

42:23.500 --> 42:26.040
I want her to take this herb

42:26.040 --> 42:28.120
and get well like magic.

42:28.120 --> 42:29.890
This herb will bring her fever down.

42:29.890 --> 42:31.380
Let's boil it carefully.

42:32.240 --> 42:33.530
So it will work magic.

42:39.490 --> 42:42.500
Can herbs like that help?

42:42.500 --> 42:44.750
We have to try everything.

42:45.370 --> 42:48.860
Whether it's medicine, herbs, or even prayer.

42:50.850 --> 42:51.910
Medical Services Team! Come in!

42:51.910 --> 42:54.310
Medical Services Team, come to the medical zone!

42:54.310 --> 42:55.580
The medicine supply truck has arrived.

42:56.210 --> 42:57.300
Copy. Over!

42:57.300 --> 42:58.270
Let's go!

43:01.390 --> 43:02.080
Hello.

43:02.080 --> 43:03.350
Thank you.

43:04.330 --> 43:05.950
Thank you.

44:05.750 --> 44:07.000
37.5 degrees.

44:28.590 --> 44:29.690
Where's Dr. Kang?

44:30.460 --> 44:31.470
I haven't seen her around.

44:32.120 --> 44:33.550
You're right.

44:34.300 --> 44:35.650
Yesterday, the local police

44:35.650 --> 44:37.160
came to arrest Fatima.

44:37.160 --> 44:39.130
So she went with them.

44:40.370 --> 44:41.610
What did you just say?

44:42.320 --> 44:44.440
Are you sure they were Uruk police officers?

46:10.650 --> 46:15.490
It's just too bad that you got hurt. What shall we do?

46:22.100 --> 46:26.030
I mean, the doctor can't treat you now.

46:27.320 --> 46:29.120
Get your hands off.

46:29.120 --> 46:31.800
Can't you see what's going on here?

46:31.800 --> 46:33.350
Do you want to die?

46:34.830 --> 46:37.030
Or do you want
to get your girlfriend killed?

46:38.680 --> 46:41.460
It's my turn to give
the orders now, Captain!

46:41.930 --> 46:45.100
The only person
these guys won't kill

46:45.330 --> 46:46.790
is me.

46:49.080 --> 46:50.560
What do you want?

46:53.330 --> 46:56.320
Finally you understand.

46:56.640 --> 46:59.120
All right. Let's talk.

47:19.700 --> 47:23.650
Weapons will be delivered

47:23.650 --> 47:25.320
to North Uruk at midnight.

47:25.320 --> 47:27.370
My own country will try to kill me once the delivery's made.

47:27.370 --> 47:31.240
But I want to survive and I want the money.

47:31.240 --> 47:34.460
So get me a way out of this country

47:34.460 --> 47:36.610
after the delivery is made tonight.

47:36.610 --> 47:39.560
That's all I want. My escape route.

47:41.620 --> 47:42.800
Come on.

47:43.180 --> 47:46.580
Save me like you did the last time, Captain.

47:47.140 --> 47:50.090
Tonight at 2:00 a.m.

47:50.090 --> 47:52.510
You can't be too early.

47:52.730 --> 47:54.520
And you can't be too late.

47:54.520 --> 47:56.640
I wouldn't want to sell her

47:56.640 --> 47:59.600
on a personal grudge.

48:01.450 --> 48:03.140
I'll kill you with my own bare hands.

48:03.780 --> 48:05.710
Upon my honor.

48:08.290 --> 48:10.590
I will kill you with my own bare hands.

48:13.230 --> 48:17.070
I'm going to learn Korean, just for you.

48:17.070 --> 48:18.060
Let's go.

48:48.790 --> 48:51.460
I have such good memories of Uruk.

48:52.460 --> 48:54.200
And you are the perfect person

48:54.200 --> 48:57.900
to spend my last night with.

49:09.320 --> 49:10.550
This is Big Boss.

49:15.150 --> 49:17.320
Mo Yeon, listen to me carefully.

49:18.900 --> 49:20.110
I'm going to find you

49:20.110 --> 49:21.420
and I'm going to rescue you.

49:27.010 --> 49:28.510
You know I'm a man of my word.

49:29.530 --> 49:31.540
I'll be there soon.

49:32.330 --> 49:33.970
Don't panic and don't cry.

49:37.300 --> 49:38.670
Hang in there.

49:40.450 --> 49:41.510
I'll be there soon.

49:53.640 --> 49:57.970
And I'm also looking forward to seeing you, Big Boss.

50:37.900 --> 50:39.360
Are you crazy?

50:41.580 --> 50:42.750
Pull yourself together.

50:43.460 --> 50:44.700
A hostage rescue?

50:45.050 --> 50:46.370
You're not Alpha Team at the moment.

50:46.940 --> 50:49.230
You're just a regular soldier.

50:49.230 --> 50:51.940
You're here to rebuild peace.

50:52.650 --> 50:53.760
I have to go.

50:55.220 --> 50:56.020
I'm leaving.

50:56.020 --> 50:57.450
You're not allowed to go anywhere!

50:57.860 --> 50:58.840
I have to go.

51:00.290 --> 51:01.140
I'll see you later.

51:01.140 --> 51:04.940
Geeze. Do you or do you not see this?

51:04.940 --> 51:07.780
This has been blinking all along.

51:07.780 --> 51:09.820
Number Two is the Commander and Number Three is the Blue House.

51:09.820 --> 51:11.470
What are you going to do?

51:20.970 --> 51:22.330
Sir. The commander of the Taebaek Unit,

51:22.330 --> 51:23.360
The first captain Park...

51:23.360 --> 51:25.350
This is the Blue House.

51:25.410 --> 51:28.920
Let me cut to the chase. Was she really kidnapped?

51:32.670 --> 51:34.720
She wasn't exactly kidnapped, but the situation...

51:34.720 --> 51:35.760
She was kidnapped.

51:36.670 --> 51:37.830
Are you sure?

51:38.190 --> 51:40.070
The CIA

51:40.070 --> 51:40.910
reported it differently.

51:40.910 --> 51:42.620
She's been kidnapped.

51:43.220 --> 51:47.740
About fifteen men were all armed...

51:47.740 --> 51:50.910
I'm going to be briefed by the US Army, so save your breath.

51:50.910 --> 51:53.130
I just called you to make sure.

51:54.180 --> 51:57.310
Until we figure out
what's exactly going on,

51:57.310 --> 51:59.020
keep quiet and stand by.

51:59.020 --> 51:59.590
Yes, sir!

51:59.590 --> 52:02.050
We have no time to stand by. We're wasting time.

52:04.610 --> 52:07.370
I'm going to follow protocol under emergency situations

52:07.370 --> 52:08.950
and carry out the hostage rescue operation.

52:09.550 --> 52:10.690
What are you saying?

52:11.350 --> 52:14.450
Didn't I just tell you to keep quiet and stand by?

52:14.690 --> 52:19.300
Hey, Captain Yoo! I let it slide when you didn't listen to me

52:19.300 --> 52:21.500
about the president of the Arab League.

52:21.500 --> 52:23.500
How dare you treat me like this?

52:24.600 --> 52:26.000
We gave you a gun

52:26.000 --> 52:27.460
to protect your country.

52:28.390 --> 52:30.890
This is not an issue of an individual living or dying.

52:31.260 --> 52:33.270
This is a national issue.

52:39.680 --> 52:41.980
If this country doesn't care about the lives

52:41.980 --> 52:43.420
of its people, I don't want to serve it.

52:44.280 --> 52:46.190
I don't know which country you serve

52:46.870 --> 52:48.730
but I'm going to protect my own country.

52:52.710 --> 52:53.780
Hey! Are you crazy?

52:56.300 --> 52:57.190
Hey! Stop there!

52:57.510 --> 52:59.310
Don't let Yoo Shi Jin leave. Stop him!

53:00.760 --> 53:04.040
Please stop! You can't leave.

53:07.000 --> 53:08.360
Is the gate sturdy?

53:09.160 --> 53:11.470
I've broken this car a few times

53:11.470 --> 53:12.640
and I can still break the gate.

53:17.170 --> 53:18.360
Please don't do this.

53:18.360 --> 53:19.700
If you don't want to get hurt, leave me alone.

53:20.830 --> 53:22.710
I'm going to drive through it.

53:23.360 --> 53:24.600
Sir!

53:28.600 --> 53:29.730
It's for you.

53:29.730 --> 53:31.000
It's Commander Yoon.

53:36.880 --> 53:38.600
Sir. Captain Yoo Shi Jin.

53:38.600 --> 53:40.400
You have three hours.

53:41.080 --> 53:43.560
For three hours, I don't know your whereabouts.

53:44.390 --> 53:45.970
For three hours,

53:45.970 --> 53:47.540
you're not part of Alpha Team

53:47.540 --> 53:49.880
or the Captain of Taeback Unit of Company Mouru

53:49.930 --> 53:51.820
or a Korean Army captain.

53:52.270 --> 53:53.460
Any objections?

53:54.330 --> 53:55.400
No, sir.

53:55.400 --> 53:56.440
That's all.

53:57.020 --> 53:58.270
Sir.

54:11.900 --> 54:13.350
How's Lieutenant Yoon?

54:13.660 --> 54:15.620
She's sleeping, but her fever is dropping.

54:16.260 --> 54:17.380
I think the medicine's kicking in.

54:18.190 --> 54:19.340
Good.

54:20.270 --> 54:22.680
I'm going out for a while.

54:24.960 --> 54:26.520
I'm sorry I can't see you before I go.

54:28.150 --> 54:29.410
I’m sorry.

54:30.900 --> 54:32.590
Going out? For what?

54:35.360 --> 54:37.360
Myung Joo's awake. I'll call you back.

54:38.270 --> 54:40.970
Anybody here?

55:05.790 --> 55:07.290
Good luck, Captain.

55:20.250 --> 55:21.270
Well done, doctor.

55:23.920 --> 55:26.800
If you need anything,
you just let me know.

55:27.060 --> 55:29.110
I don't know why you brought me here.

55:29.810 --> 55:31.730
But if you want ransom, forget it.

55:32.690 --> 55:34.950
I have more debt than money.

55:47.990 --> 55:49.300
In English.

55:51.460 --> 55:53.610
I can't have you think
that I'm a nice guy.

55:54.270 --> 55:56.760
Especially if I'm holding a gun.

55:56.940 --> 55:59.070
Now how many times have I told you?

55:59.070 --> 56:01.150
You're more likely to get shot

56:01.680 --> 56:03.680
being around a guy with a gun.

56:17.650 --> 56:23.060
Big Boss. He's smart, funny...

56:25.470 --> 56:27.150
And mysterious.

56:28.940 --> 56:30.350
But he has a lot of secrets.

56:30.550 --> 56:33.340
He'll disappear from time to time

56:33.980 --> 56:38.860
and be hard to contact.

56:39.720 --> 56:41.520
And then one day...

56:46.250 --> 56:48.700
He'll never come back.

56:55.890 --> 56:57.290
You should break up with him now.

57:02.630 --> 57:04.260
This is advice.

57:05.380 --> 57:06.860
Not a warning.

57:15.470 --> 57:17.800
You're supposed to offer an envelope full of money

57:17.800 --> 57:19.130
and a glass of water
in this kind of situation.

57:20.480 --> 57:22.340
You can't just make demands.

57:24.330 --> 57:26.620
You're dying to know
what I'm saying, aren't you?

57:27.680 --> 57:29.400
You don't need to know,

57:30.050 --> 57:31.450
you piece of garbage!

57:33.940 --> 57:36.100
You are not easy.

57:37.480 --> 57:39.290
Big Boss! Big Boss! Please come in!

57:39.290 --> 57:41.300
Big Boss! Please come in!

57:49.760 --> 57:50.460
Sir.

57:50.460 --> 57:51.640
When did Captain Yoo leave?

57:51.640 --> 57:54.380
He went through the gate at 17:30.

57:54.380 --> 57:55.590
Where's Dr. Kang?

57:55.590 --> 57:57.610
Well...

57:57.610 --> 57:58.940
She went to the local police station last night.

57:59.270 --> 58:00.520
But she hasn't come back yet.

58:03.700 --> 58:06.060
What happened?

58:09.430 --> 58:11.420
Something really bad.

58:24.770 --> 58:26.060
It's been a while.

58:28.350 --> 58:30.530
Long time no talk.

58:30.530 --> 58:32.180
Is everything okay?

58:32.180 --> 58:35.370
Let me use your last card.

58:37.290 --> 58:39.880
I need a chopper.

58:41.440 --> 58:44.110
I have a date to keep.

59:21.490 --> 59:24.670
-=Next Episode-=

59:31.460 --> 59:32.460
Drop the gun!

59:39.690 --> 59:40.850
Let's go.
